<dtccode>P0630</dtccode>
<dtcname>VIN not Programmed or Mismatch - ECM / PCM</dtcname>
<subpara id="RM000000PGD00BX_01" type-id="60" category="03" proc-id="RM0250U___00002QO00000">
<name>DESCRIPTION</name>
<content5 releasenbr="1">
<ptxt>DTC P0630 is set when the Vehicle Identification Number (VIN) is not stored in the Engine Control Module (ECM) or the input VIN is not accurate. Input the VIN with the intelligent tester.						 						</ptxt>
